Business Objective:
Each Salesperson will be assigned with a Target (no of products to be sold) for each month. Which is given to them based on their last month's Achievement (no of products sold) i.e. 10% Increased from the last achievement.

Data Set Details:
-We can implement a model to predict the target given to them for the next month based on their previous achievement instead of giving them simply a 10% hike.
-Data set details sent in csv file. 

